room_title: Escape room "Doll House V.2" by PuzzleMazement in Los Angeles
room_address: 1238 S Beach Blvd D, Anaheim, CA 92804
room_description: Gianna and Ryan dreamed of living a happy married life together.  They didn't know Gianna's doll, Little Brother, had other plans for them.  Your team must rescue the bride and groom from the powers of Little Brother before the hour is up and your team is turned into porcelain to join the doll collection.
